{"tid":517930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"本身有得搞變到無得搞","createTime":"2018-01-02T19:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T19:12:45.000Z","uid":148192,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db5f1da5e5ae344a92dd6e6271e53aa5d9c06d54","tid":517930,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T19:27:56.000Z","msg":"呢排係IG識咗條女，個樣好純，望上去陣處味仲係度。<br />\n<br />\n可能我靚仔關係，同佢傾咗無耐我將話題慢慢轉落咸野度，就黎撩到佢出黎扑野時，佢問我一句會唔會太快？ 同埋...你呢啲靚仔一定唔會係處... 咁樣對我唔公平..<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌，我呃唔到自己，因為到而家先發現，原來一個處對男性黎講都好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n唔係話聖人mode, 只係以後每次同唔同女搞野我都會諗清楚。  究竟我咁做啱唔啱，會唔會之後後悔。"},{"pid":"eda61862dd7107397289903190e952cad7fc80c6","tid":517930,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T19:33:17.000Z","msg":"我真係好想搞你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cf8bd5e6968830a73f85386ea7e62a8afb62b5","tid":517930,"uid":41737,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T19:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d069ba5e359b876208f40e9ed1d317744018da6","tid":517930,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9cf8bd5e6968830a73f85386ea7e62a8afb62b5","tid":517930,"uid":41737,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T19:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T19:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035d071f0bf1c20b2d05d73a749ddd813e416a90","tid":517930,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T19:35:17.000Z","msg":"usb"},{"pid":"a557927fb54b160c3fedf8985b05f6667e3c176a","tid":517930,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T20:54:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68061f2712feb49326819b75d0545044eae30e96","tid":517930,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,